Hey everyone it's been awhile since I wrote to the list. 

I think a big thing is that most bus people wave to each other as a sign of
comradarie. You don't find that with 98 percent of the people in 98 percent
of the cars these days. We all feel a kinship. I notice it with bug people,
older Porsche car people, and other very unique car people.

